# Admin API URL
# This is the full API URL for a specific store you have created in your admin dashboard.
#
# How to get this value:
# 1. Deploy your admin application (e.g., to Vercel).
# 2. Open your deployed admin dashboard and create a new store.
# 3. Navigate to that store's "Settings" page.
# 4. Copy the store ID from the browser's URL bar (it's the long string of characters).
# 5. Construct the full URL like the example below.
#
# Example: https://my-admin-app.vercel.app/api/xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL="https://YOUR_DEPLOYED_ADMIN_URL/api/YOUR_STORE_ID"